<dl id="n12188m"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12188m">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12188m"> 188(m)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> Salesian ~</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">THE secondary title of this important and attractive survey of the &ldquo;<mark>Salesian</mark> methods&rdquo; expresses its policy and scope. M. l&apos;Abbe Vincent, whose book is a rare combination of erudition and of spirituality at once definite and large-minded, has written here for all educators that take their duties in the higher way, a work of permanent value. <small> T.C., review of &ldquo;Saint Francis de Sales&rdquo; <a name="SFDS" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#SFDS"><cite title="source">Studies</cite></a> (June 1924) 331</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
